annotation.TEXT: Hey there everyone, and welcome back to Super Ninji Jump Fighter Alpha 3 Turbo! Wait, that isn't right... It's just Ninji Jump Alpha, but you gotta scream it, like this...
Gold berry count: 4
And, I apparently sucked at jumping there.

Alright, let's go check out the next level, Reznor Ruins. Gee, I wonder who the boss will be? (Ooh! I know! It's Roy right?)
